OL,7,FGranada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef went to visit the homeless
OL,9,Fcharity which faces losing its home.
OL,11,FA charity which has saved thousands of
OL,12,Fpeople from sleeping rough - say it
OL,13,Fnow faces being made homeless itself.
OL,15,FEmmaus has been operating from its 26-
OL,16,Fbedroom base in Salford for 12 years,
OL,17,Fbut its lease has run out and Salford
OL,18,FCity Council has earmarked the site
OL,19,Ffor development.
