OL,7,FIt has been unable to find new
OL,8,Fpremises and say it is now existing on
OL,9,Fborrowed time, even though Salford
OL,10,FCouncil says it is working with the
OL,11,Fcharity to find new premises in the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FThose the charity has helped out of
OL,15,Fhomelessness say, if it has to close,
OL,16,Fthey will end up back on the streets.
