OL,7,FJohn Moir, who had been homeless for
OL,8,Fyears, was helped by Emmaus after
OL,9,Fliving under a hedgerow in wasteland
OL,10,Fjust outside the centre of Manchester
OL,11,Fhome for five weeks.
OL,13,FHe said: "I was here for five weeks
OL,14,Fevery night. When I used to get up in
OL,15,Fthe morning I used to walk from here
OL,16,Fto the city centre to try and get some
OL,17,Ffood.
