OL,7,F"I felt suicidal a few times but in my
OL,8,Fmind I would never do it myself but
OL,9,Fthe thought has been there, thinking
OL,10,Fthis is the end."
OL,12,FNow aged 57, John volunteers at the
OL,13,FEmmaus Salford charity shop, helping
OL,14,Fothers furnish their homes and in
OL,15,Freturn has a room for as long as he
OL,16,Fneeds it as well as access to support
OL,17,Fand job training
OL,19,F"I feel safe and secure here. I do
OL,20,Fhave a good nights sleep when I do get
OL,21,Fmy head down," he said.
