OL,7,FAnd if the site had to close he has no
OL,8,Fdoubt what would happen to him: "I'd
OL,9,Fprobably be back to square one again.
OL,11,F"I'd probably end up back on the
OL,12,Fstreet which is going back down the
OL,13,Fladder isnt it. I want to go up the
OL,14,Fladder. That is what I'm trying for."
OL,16,FIan Willams is now the resident cook
OL,17,Fat Emmaus, feeding 20-plus people
OL,18,Fevery evening, and spent a year on the
OL,19,Fstreets, during which he was assaulted.
