OL,7,F"I got attacked a couple of times," he
OL,8,Fsaid. "That's how I lost my top teeth.
OL,9,FI wasn't begging. I was just out of
OL,10,Fthe way and some lads came round and
OL,11,Fsaid 'oh look at that so and so' and
OL,12,Flet rip.
OL,14,F"Emmaus saved me. This place saved me.
OL,15,FI don't think I would be here
OL,16,Fotherwise."
OL,18,FJackie Smith, CEO of Emmaus, predicted
OL,19,Fa grim future for the building's
OL,20,Fresidents if no alternative premises
OL,21,Fcould be found.
