OL,5,Chousing
OL,7,F"They'll be back to street
OL,8,Fhomelessness," she said. "That would
OL,9,Fbe the only option for them. There's
OL,10,Fjust not the services out there -
OL,11,Fthere is not the accommodation out
OL,12,Fthere.
OL,14,F"It would be street homeless for the
OL,15,Fmajority if not all."
OL,17,FCouncillor Tracy Kelly, Deputy City
OL,18,FMayor and Lead Member for Housing,
OL,19,FProperty and Regeneration, said the
OL,20,Fcouncil recognised the 'amazing' work
OL,21,FEmmaus did.
