OL,7,FShe added: "Alongside their and other
OL,8,Fcharities work in the city, the
OL,9,Fcouncil is committed to delivering our
OL,10,Fgoal of providing quality affordable
OL,11,Fhousing, to help alleviate the housing
OL,12,Fcrisis the city is currently facing.
OL,14,F"The council is committed to
OL,15,Fdelivering the regeneration of
OL,16,FPendleton including building 500 much
OL,17,Fneeded affordable homes.
