OL,7,F"Whilst plans for this part of the
OL,8,FPendleton are still being drawn up we
OL,9,Fhave agreed that Emmaus could utilise
OL,10,Fan empty council building on a
OL,11,Ftemporary basis until the site is
OL,12,Fredeveloped.
OL,14,F"We have started and will continue to
OL,15,Fwork closely with Emmaus and will do
OL,16,Fall we can to support them in finding
OL,17,Fa suitable alternative location in the
OL,18,Fcity."
